---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "How many tributes can participate in a Hunger Games Simulation?",
    answer: "You can add between 5 to 24 tributes in a single simulation. This flexibility allows you to create both intimate and grand-scale games."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I customize tribute attributes?",
    answer: "You can customize the content of the Hunger Games emulator and leave a message under my <a href='https://x.com/liarpzu' class='text-blue-400 hover:underline'>X/Twitter</a>, and I will update the relevant features as soon as possible."
  },
  {
    question: "How long does a Hunger Games Simulator take?",
    answer: "A simulation can be completed in just a few minutes, though you can adjust the pace and detail level of events to your preference."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I save and share my Hunger Games Simulation results?",
    answer: "Yes, each Hunger Games simulation generates a unique story that you can save and share with others, including detailed event logs and the victor's journey."
  }
];
---

<section id="faq" class="py-24 bg-secondary-light">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Find answers to common questions about the Hunger Games Simulator.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        {faqs.map(faq => (
          <div class="bg-secondary p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">{faq.question}</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70" set:html={faq.answer}></p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>